metadata.name: FPTP Media Perpetual Ad #1
metadata.description: A community-driven multimedia brand founded by MISHKAcreates. Each Perpetual Ad allows its owner to advertise on various forms of From Porches To Porsches media at no additional cost. MISHKAcreates is an American-based designer and business owner, who founded FPTP Media in 2019. FPTP Media is a gritty community of business owners and investors that use their automotive passion to fuel their financial success.
